#: FUNCTION ^G(no arguments)^g
#:   Dewrap CPAN

function f-cpan {
	sparkle <<-===SPARKLE===
	  Did you mean ^Tcpan^t^K{3}m^k?
	  If you actually want to run ^BCPAN^b, use
	    ^Tcommand cpan ^U…^u^t
	===SPARKLE===
}

